Creating a Telegram bot with Python
🔑 STEP 1: Create a Bot on Telegram (Token)
Open Telegram
Search for BotFather
Start the chat and type: /start   /newbot
Give your bot , name , username
📦 STEP 2: Install Required Python Library
pip install python-telegram-bot
🧪 STEP 3: Write Your First Bot Code
bot.py
▶️ STEP 4: Run the Bot
python bot.py
💬 STEP 5: Test Your Bot




